#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Gunslinger Mod"
msgstr "枪手模组"

#. ~ Description for Gunslinger Mod
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds a bionic and a non bionic variant of a gunslinger profession. Become "
"the fastest gun in the cataclysm."
msgstr "添加了生化与非生化两种变体的枪手职业。成为大灾变中最快的枪。"
